                        <p>Would you like to join our Endurance team ? We have been out of action this year due to injury but plans are in place to get in training for 2015. Cromwell Endurance Group are in the process of putting together a super training program which will give a great insight into the world of endurance. This would be an ideal opportunity to come along and meet other endurance riders &amp; find out more about this fun sport and join the HDRC team. You may even qualify to ride the World famous Red Dragon across the Welsh mountains. Contact Susan Durman if interested.</p>
